title: Sujal Sarangdhar - Resume
summary: Sujal Sarangdhar is a skilled Software Developer with expertise in Python, Django, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Java. With experience at Tega IT Solutions PVT. Sujal possesses strong technical skills in various programming languages, version control, modern web technologies, AI/ML concepts, and database management. They hold certifications in AWS Cloud Practitioner and Core Java, complemented by robust soft skills and social engagements in related fields.
